perturbations.original:
\begin{equation}
    \label{eq: prop sphere gen}
    \norm{A/B}^2
    = \max_{v \in \bb R^d \setminus\{0\}} \;
    \frac{\scp{v}{A^{\tT}A v}}{\scp{v}{B^{\tT}B v}}
    = \max_{v \in \bb S^{d-1}} \;
    \frac{\scp{v}{A^{\tT}A v}}{\scp{v}{B^{\tT}B v}}
    = \max_{v \in \bb S_{B^{\tT}B}^{d-1}} \;
    \scp{v}{A^{\tT}A v}.
\end{equation}

perturbations.perturbed:
